    <briefdescription>
<para>Wave square (x, y) function class. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This class models a wave square function with specific noise wavenumbers, rotation angle, and phase shift. It extends the base <ref refid="classhmap_1_1Function" kindref="compound">Function</ref> class. </para>
